#: ../../source/textarea_detection_and_text_reinjection.rst:2
msgid "文字区域检测和译文回填"
msgstr "Text area detection and translation backfilling"


#: ../../source/textarea_detection_and_text_reinjection.rst:4
msgid "ImageTrans实现了一套文字区域检测和译文回填方法。"
msgstr "ImageTrans implements a set of text area detection and translation backfilling methods."


#: ../../source/textarea_detection_and_text_reinjection.rst:7
msgid "文字区域检测"
msgstr "Text area detection"


#: ../../source/textarea_detection_and_text_reinjection.rst:9
msgid "点击编辑-自动定位文字（启发式），将获得所有候选文字区域"
msgstr "Click Edit-Auto-Target Text (Heuristic) to get all candidate text areas"


#: ../../source/textarea_detection_and_text_reinjection.rst:10
msgid "点击编辑-文字区域操作-获取文字区域置信度，文字区域可能性较低的区域的文本框颜色将变为黄色。这类区域可以自行去除或者隐藏，但因为有些区域被误识别为非文字区域，去除的话翻译时还要手动框选，建议不要直接去除。"
msgstr "Click Edit-Text Area Action - Get the confidence level of the text area, and the text box color in the less likely area of the text will turn yellow. This type of area can be removed or hidden by itself, but because some areas are mistakenly identified as non-text areas, the removal of the translation should also be manually boxed, it is not recommended to remove directly."


#: ../../source/textarea_detection_and_text_reinjection.rst:11
msgid "选择文字区域进行OCR和翻译，操作结束后，可以点击编辑-文字区域操作去除没有原文或者没有译文的区域。"
msgstr "Select the text area for OCR and translation, and after the operation, you can click the Edit-Text area action to remove areas without the original text or without a translation."


#: ../../source/textarea_detection_and_text_reinjection.rst:15
msgid "OCR等操作会自动略过文字区域可能性较低的区域。"
msgstr "Operations such as OCR automatically skip areas where the text area is less likely."


#: ../../source/textarea_detection_and_text_reinjection.rst:17
msgid "因为不同的漫画尺寸不同，需要设置不同的文字区域检测参数，可以在项目-设置-文字区域检测里进行设置。"
msgstr "Because different comic sizes vary, different text area detection parameters need to be set, which can be set in the item-setting-text area detection."


#: ../../source/textarea_detection_and_text_reinjection.rst:19
msgid ""
"文字区域检测的算法细节见此：`基于规则的漫画文字检测方法 <http://blog.xulihang.me/text-localization-"
"for-comics/>`_"
msgstr "The algorithm details of text area detection can be found here: `Rules-based comic text detection method <http://blog.xulihang.me/text-localization-for-comics/>`_"


#: ../../source/textarea_detection_and_text_reinjection.rst:21
msgid ""
"文字区域置信度获取是利用Tensorflow提供的脚本基于卷积神经网络预训练模型重新训练的，相关代码见此： "
"`<https://github.com/xulihang/text-image-classifier>`_。"
msgstr "Text area confidence acquisition is retrained using the script provided by Tensorflow based on convolutional neural network pre-training models, and the relevant code can be found here: `<https://github.com/xulihang/text-image-classifier>`_."


#: ../../source/textarea_detection_and_text_reinjection.rst:23
msgid "文字区域检测的操作本工具提供手动分步操作功能，操作方式是菜单栏-编辑-文字区域操作以及右侧编辑区的合并上下区域和合并左右区域按钮。"
msgstr "The action tool for text area detection provides manual step-by-step operation by way of menu bar-edit-text area operation and the merge upper and lower area and merge left and right area buttons of the right editing area."


#: ../../source/textarea_detection_and_text_reinjection.rst:27
msgid "译文回填"
msgstr "Backfilling"


#: ../../source/textarea_detection_and_text_reinjection.rst:29
msgid "译文回填分为两步，一步是原文抹除，一步是译文的放置。"
msgstr "Backfilling is divided into two steps, one step is the original erase, one step is the placement of the translation."


#: ../../source/textarea_detection_and_text_reinjection.rst:32
msgid "原文抹除"
msgstr "Original erasing"


#: ../../source/textarea_detection_and_text_reinjection.rst:34
msgid "原文抹除有两种模式，一种是精确模式，一种是非精确模式。"
msgstr "There are two modes of original erasing, one is the precision mode and the other is the inexact mode."


#: ../../source/textarea_detection_and_text_reinjection.rst:36
msgid ""
"精确模式下，会先生成文字掩膜，再根据掩膜进行图像修复。如果掩膜生成不正确，可以使用编辑-生成/编辑掩膜进行修改，掩膜图像会保存在图片目录，带有mask后缀"
"，而去除文字的图像则带有text-"
"removed后缀。如果掩膜没有手动生成，每次预览时会自动生成，会耗费时间进行计算。需要注意的一点是浅色字体区域，需要先设置背景颜色和文字颜色，程序判断文字颜色比背景颜色浅时会对图像颜色做反转，这样文字掩膜才能够生成。"
msgstr "In precise mode, Mr. Will form a text mask, and then according to the mask for image repair. If the mask is generated incorrectly, it can be modified using the Edit-Build/Edit mask, and the mask image is saved in the picture catalog with a mask suffix, while the text-removed image has a text-removed suffix. If the mask is not generated manually, it is automatically generated at each preview and takes time to calculate. One thing to note is that the light font area, you need to set the background color and text color first, the program determines that the text color is lighter than the background color will reverse the image color, so that the text mask can be generated."


#: ../../source/textarea_detection_and_text_reinjection.rst:38
msgid "非精确模式下，则会使用背景颜色生成一个文本框进行遮盖。这一模式较适合背景单一的数字图像。"
msgstr "In imprecise mode, a text box is used to generate a text box to mask. This pattern is more suitable for a single digital image with a background."


#: ../../source/textarea_detection_and_text_reinjection.rst:40
msgid "下图是掩膜编辑器："
msgstr "The following image is the mask editor:"


#: ../../source/textarea_detection_and_text_reinjection.rst:45
msgid "译文放置"
msgstr "Translation placement"


#: ../../source/textarea_detection_and_text_reinjection.rst:47
msgid "根据文本框的大小和位置放置译文，支持自动根据文本框的大小调整译文大小，可以在项目设置里进行设置。"
msgstr "Depending on the size and location of the text box, you support automatically resize the translation based on the size of the text box, which you can set in the project settings."


#: ../../source/textarea_detection_and_text_reinjection.rst:51
msgid "颜色检测"
msgstr "Color detection"


#: ../../source/textarea_detection_and_text_reinjection.rst:53
msgid "本工具能较粗略地自动检测背景颜色和文字颜色，点击编辑-颜色操作进行相关操作。"
msgstr "This tool can be a rough and automatic detection of background color and text color, click edit-color operation to carry out related operations."


